✦ Version v1.2.5 - The Problem-Centric Optimization

Since v1.2.0, we have completely overhauled the internal data architecture to move from a "Flat Attempt Log" to a sophisticated "Problem-Centric Nested Structure." This ensures maximum data integrity and performance.

Major Changes in v1.2.5:

1. Problem-Centric Data Architecture (Storage Optimization)
   * Nested Submissions: Individual attempts (submissions) are now grouped inside their parent Problem object. 
   * Zero Redundancy: Problem metadata (Name, URL, Tags, Difficulty) is stored only once per problem instead of repeated for every attempt.
   * Faster Analytics: The Deep Analytics modal now reads directly from the nested structure, making it lightning-fast even with hundreds of attempts.
   * Seamless Migration: Automated logic that converts your old flat history into the new optimized format without data loss.

2. Enhanced Tagging & Synchronization
   * Real-time Sync: Adding or removing a tag from any problem (active or historical) instantly synchronizes that tag across all instances of that problem.
   * Global Consistency: Your problem tags are now a true "source of truth" across the entire extension.

3. Refined Multi-Select Tag Filtering
   * Smart Search: The history tag filter now automatically excludes already-selected tags from the dropdown list.
   * Removable Badges: Active filters now appear as small, high-contrast badges with an "×" button for quick removal.
   * Quick Drill-down: Clicking any tag in the Stats tab's distribution list instantly applies that single tag filter in the History view.

4. UI & Performance Polish
   * Fixed Chart Flickering: Optimized the Stats tab refresh logic to update text values live without re-rendering the charts every second.
   * Better Light Mode: Improved contrast for analytics modals, trend charts, and status badges in light theme.
   * Responsive Adjustments: Fine-tuned popup spacing and footer size to maximize vertical space.

5. Production Readiness
   * Updated manifest.json to v1.2.5.
   * Re-build production package dist/green-timer-v1.2.5.zip.

This version represents the most stable and performant release of Green Timer to date.
